### 6️⃣ Consulta SQL

```sql
SELECT  
    DATENAME(dw, lpepPickupDatetime) AS Day,
    AVG(tripDistance) AS AvgDistance
FROM taxi_rides
GROUP BY DATENAME(dw, lpepPickupDatetime)
